{"tid":429424,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曾言'共產黨好偉大' 律師會前會長林新強　擬選港區人大","createTime":"2017-10-09T01:28:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-09T05:08:05.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"67ad5f2bab8b4aacc6b2d15d82da29d1f054da1e","tid":429424,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T01:28:27.000Z","msg":"港區全國人大年底換屆，《經濟日報》政情專欄報道，律師會前會長林新強，亦積極考慮出戰，專欄指林新強除有意參選港區人大外，亦有機會獲委任為全國政協委員。<br />\n<br />\n《經濟日報》專欄又指出，有政界中人指，中央一直希望港區人大代表及政協委員可以積極發聲，料日後本港有不少具爭議性的議題，都涉及複雜的法律問題，例如國歌法於本港立法、一地兩檢以至港獨等，因此有法律資格人士參選人大會有一定優勢。<br />\n<br />\n林新強任職律師會長期間，曾為一國兩制白皮書護航，認同法官愛國無問題，不影響司法獨立，之後更曾言「我覺得共產黨係好偉大」，引起法律界嘩然。香港律師會在2014年舉行特別會員大會，在2392票支持、1478票反對下，大比數通過對會長林新強的不信任動議，令林成為首名被「不信任」的律師會會長，林之後辭任律師會主席一職。<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1-%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E6%9C%83%E5%89%8D%E6%9C%83%E9%95%B7%E6%9E%97%E6%96%B0%E5%BC%B7-%E6%93%AC%E9%81%B8%E6%B8%AF%E5%8D%80%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%A7/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E5%25BE%258B%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%2589%258D%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%259E%2597%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25BC%25B7-%25E6%2593%25AC%25E9%2581%25B8%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%258D%2580%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A4%25A7%2F&d=S%2BzA7th1L7UoSqlz9XCkIJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=e8855d53\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E5%25BE%258B%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%2589%258D%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%259E%2597%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25BC%25B7-%25E6%2593%25AC%25E9%2581%25B8%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%258D%2580%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A4%25A7%2F&h=be31c991\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1-%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E6%9C%83%E5%89%8D%E6%9C%83%E9%95%B7%E6%9E%97%E6%96%B0%E5%BC%B7-%E6%93%AC%E9%81%B8%E6%B8%AF%E5%8D%80%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%A7/</a>"},{"pid":"564d28f5af9053e42923ba4160b43e1c59840593","tid":429424,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T01:30:54.000Z","msg":"又係咪個行得太前既例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e01c2cf2b18a9b6190d72fe5cedb7b416aebf6aa","tid":429424,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T05:06:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Oct8近期活躍五毛<br />\nJR<br />\n三色貓<br />\n民國復興<br />\n曼徹斯特聯=拜仁慕尼黑<br />\n蘇麗珊<br />\n國語好手<br />\nbb chu<br />\nRedbaron<br />\nnewlife<br />\n優美開始<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"0d3d9e094dadfc2ec108f0c3f2b5de732e9ed148","tid":429424,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T05:08:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又係咪個行得太前既例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大佬擦鞋擦到五毛三色貓咁低質真係好尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}